 font-medium\">\n              Sign in\n            </Button>\n          </form>\n          <p className=\"mt-6 text-sm text-muted-foreground dark:text-muted-foreground\">\n            Forgot your password?{\" \"}\n            <a\n              href=\"#\"\n              className=\"font-medium text-primary hover:text-primary/90 dark:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary/90\"\n            >\n              Reset password\n            </a>\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"
